    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine Domini amen. Breve descripsi causa memorie qualiter facta est
                        in loco et finibus <placeName ref="#places/318" key="#Houses #Roads"
                            >Paterno</placeName> in <rs key="#Roads">via publica</rs>, in presentia
                        bonorum hominum quorum nomina inferius leguntur. <persName><name
                                ref="Portatus de Paterno">Portatus</name> de Paterno</persName> per
                        meum sacramentum sic designa (sic) terram <orgName key="#Hospitals"><rs
                                key="#Hospitals">hospitalis</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Hospitals" ref="#places/3207"
                            >Tepasci</placeName></orgName> quam ego teneo et mei consorte detinent
                        (sic) a predicto hospitale in <placeName ref="#places/318"
                            >Paterno</placeName> et meis finibus. Prima petia cum <rs key="#Houses"
                            >abiturio</rs> et capanna supra se et infra se habente tenet unum caput
                        in terra dicti hospitalis Teopasci que est recta et laborata per
                                <persName><name ref="Heinricus">Henrigum</name></persName> quondam
                        ***, aliut in terra de<orgName key="#Monasteries">
                            <rs key="#Monasteries">batia</rs> de <placeName key="#Monasteries"
                                ref="#places/3200">Ficeclo</placeName></orgName> que est recta et
                        laborata per <persName><name ref="Bacalare">Bacalare</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Talis">Talis</name></persName>, latus in via
                        publica, aliut in terra dicte abatie et in terra dicti hospitalis. Secunda
                        petia tenet unum caput in Arno, aliut vero caput in via publica, latus unum
                        tenet in terra <persName><name ref="Grecus">Grechi</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Martinus">Martini</name></persName>, aliut vero
                        latus in terra dicte abbatie. Hoc totum designamentum ego Portatus facio ad
                        honore Dei et beati Iachopi apostoli et reverentia ipsius hospitalis Tepasci
                        et domini <persName><name ref="Ildebrandinus">Ildebrandini</name></persName>
                        magistri et rectori eiusdem hospitalis. Per meum sacramentum sic
                        terrefinatum habeo (dictam terram) in presentia et testimonio <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Mainectus">Mainecti</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Advocatus"><name ref="Rodelandus"
                                >Rolandi</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Guicciardus">Guiciardi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Advocatus">advocati</rs> dicti hospitalis, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Bordo">Bordone</name></persName> quondam
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Bernardus"
                            >Bernardi</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Quintavallus">Quintavalle</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Deotifece">Deotifeci</name></persName> germani
                        et quondam <persName><name ref="Datodeus">Datidei</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Bacatellus"
                            >Bacatelli</name></persName> atque <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Pescator de Potho">Pescatoris</name></persName> de <placeName
                            ref="#places/3210">Pottho</placeName> et aliorum <rs key="#Witness"
                            >testium</rs>. Dominus dictus Ildebrandinus, rector dicti hospitalis,
                        hoc designamentum fecit fieri dominice incarnationis anno millesimo
                        centesimo nonagesimo octavo, duodecimo kalendas aprelis, indictione prima.
                        (S) Ego <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Wiselbertus"
                                >Guisalbertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domni imperatoris ibi fui et hoc breve
                        fideliter <rs key="#Writer">scripsi</rs>.</ab>
                </div>
